videos.description: Cassius Winston drives hard on the baseline and goes up to bank in a difficult reverse layup among the outstretched arms of the Michigan defense.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Winston makes difficult baseline reverse layup) 2020/01/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Winston makes difficult baseline reverse layup

videos.description: Cassius Winston drives to the basket and tosses up a lob over his head to Xavier Tillman, who hangs on to the rim after throwing down a dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Winston lobs to Tillman for the slam) 2020/01/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Winston lobs to Tillman for the slam
